---
title: Sweet Potato Lentil Sheppy Pie with Roasted Tenderstem®
description: We love a good Sweet Potato Topped Lentil Sheppy Pie and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-lentil-sheppy-pie-09c16671-c3b6fa78.jpg
